Ghost - Class in entrants.ghosts.username
This class serves as a base class for the ghosts Each ghost has a knowledge about its environment (The topology of the level, the other ghosts, the nodes containing pills/power pills) and the PacMan The knowledge of a ghost can be visualized using GraphStream.
